Beautify your x login screen
	
xbanner is a program designed to beautify your x login screen.
it can draw text and render some effect on it, and it can fill
the background with a nice pattern of colors. xbanner can also
put an image on the screen for you, as well as do some minimal
animation.

xbanner works with all three x display managers packaged for debian:
xdm, gdm & wdm.